  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Specifies the behavior of the managed disk when the VM gets deleted, for
            example whether the managed disk is deleted or detached. Supported values
            are: **Delete.** If this value is used, the managed disk is deleted when
            VM gets deleted. **Detach.** If this value is used, the managed disk is
            retained after VM gets deleted. Minimum api-version: 2021-03-01.
            </summary>
